Question: Do you think it is worthwhile to invest in space exploration?
Answer:
I do think it is worthwhile to invest in space exploration even if it may seem unpractical or may take resources away from other important projects.  Space exploration is important for the development of telecommunications. We all know the value of telecommunications under the impact of globalization. Second, space exploration can help to trace human and earth history. Finally, it is a great way to be prepared for future disaster.